query:
SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM cat_aka_name_1 AS an,
   cat_char_name_1 AS chn,
   cat_cast_info_1 AS ci,
   cat_company_name_1 AS cn,
   cat_info_type_1 AS it,
  cat_movie_companies_1 AS mc,
   cat_movie_info_1 AS mi,
   cat_name_1 AS n,
   cat_role_type_1 AS rt,
   cat_title_1 AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND t.id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND cn.id = mc.company_id
AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
AND n.id = ci.person_id
AND rt.id = ci.role_id
AND n.id = an.person_id
AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)')
AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
AND it.info = 'release dates'
AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2006)%' OR mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%')
AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND n.name LIKE '%G%'
AND rt.role = 'actress'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1990 AND 2008;

FROM cat_aka_name_1 AS an,
   cat_char_name_1 AS chn,
   cat_cast_info_1 AS ci,
   cat_company_name_1 AS cn,
   cat_info_type_1 AS it,
  cat_movie_companies_1 AS mc,
   cat_movie_info_1 AS mi,
   cat_name_1 AS n,
   cat_role_type_1 AS rt,
   cat_title_1 AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND t.id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND cn.id = mc.company_id
AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
AND n.id = ci.person_id
AND rt.id = ci.role_id
AND n.id = an.person_id
AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)')
AND cn.country_code = '[nl]'
AND it.info = 'release dates'
AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
AND (mc.note LIKE '%(2007)%' OR mc.note LIKE '%(co-production)%')
AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%' OR mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%2007%')
AND n.gender = 'm'
AND n.name LIKE '%F%'
AND rt.role = 'actor'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2010;

   cat_cast_info_1 AS ci,

WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mc.movie_id
AND t.id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND cn.id = mc.company_id

AND n.id = ci.person_id
